Title: Fitting Bayesian Poisson Regression
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2021-09-04
Author: Laura D'Angelo, Antonio Canale
Maintainer: Laura D'Angelo <laura.dangelo@live.com>
Description: Posterior sampling and inference for Bayesian Poisson regression models. The model specification makes use of Gaussian (or conditionally Gaussian) prior distributions on the regression coefficients. 
